title: Outlaws of the Rio Grand (1941) TIM McCOY

sources.title: Outlaws of the Rio Grand (1941) TIM McCOY
sources.description:
Stars: Tim McCoy, Virginia Carpenter, Rex Lease
Director: Sam Newfield

U.S. Marshal Tim Barton infiltrates a gang of counterfeiters. But the heroic lawman inadvertently shows his hand when he falls in love with the engraver's pretty daughter, Rita. Tim will have to act fast if he and Rita are to escape from the gang with their lives.
